                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18011028-5-off24 t18011028-5-cd25"></join>, twenty-five waistcoats, value 6l. 5s. the property of 
                     <persName id="t18011028-5-victim80" type="victimName">
                        John 
                        Tine
                     <interp inst="t18011028-5-victim80" type="surname" value="Tine"></interp>
